# Twitter

Simple API to add, fetch and search tweets.

## Add tweet [/add]

### Add a new tweet [POST]

Add a new tweet specifying author's user ID and tweet text

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "user": "5adFgtu23_564aSbmogr346h0q",
            "text": "Hello world!"
        }
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "ok": "true",
            "result": {
                "_id": "12dfdbGRqaS34D5Hth5PaXsw",
                "text": "Hello World!",
                "published": "2015-08-05T08:40:51.620Z",
                "user": {
                    "_id": "5adFgtu23_564aSbmogr346h0q",
                    "username": "pincopallino",
                    "name": "Pinco",
                    "surname": "Pallino"
                    }
                }
        }
        
+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
            "ok": "false",
            "error_code": 400,
            "description": "Missing parameter(s)"
        }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

        {
            "ok": "false",
            "error_code": 500,
            "description": "Something went wrong"
        }

