## Fetch new tweets of a specific user [/fetch/{username}]

### Get all new tweets of a specific user [GET]

Get all new tweets made by a specific user

+ Parameters
    - username: Tweet author's username
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "ok": "true",
